_sText:
Each team has a generator that can blow up. The objective is to blow up the enemies team generator across the way which kills everyone on that team, or just eliminate all the oposing players. Works well with any amount of people and actualy is also a great 1v1 map.

Map made a while ago releasing now
Set for up to 32 spawns
